Package: liftchart
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Creating Cumulative Gain and Lift Charts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Arman", "Radmanesh", , "radmanesh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0009-0007-5305-9689"))
Description: Provides functions to calculate and plot cumulative gain and lift charts for evaluating predictive models.
    The package is designed to work with the `dplyr` package, `rlang` and the `ggplot2` package.
